target.comment:
1) Pasture and Forest Users Associations are established in both project pilot regions;
2) Carbon pool calculated for forest and pasture in both pilot regions;
3) Forest inventory of both regions are conducted.

actual.comment:
1) Establishmen of Pasture and Forest Users Associations were initiated in both project pilot regions, in Ismayilly and in Shemakha
2) In both pilot regions carbon pool was calculated for forest areas;
3) Forest inventory for both regions were initiated.

indicator.description:
1) Multi-sectoral/multi-stakeholder working group is effectively established;
2) National targets in response to the global Aichi Targets are developed;
3) NBSAP for Azerbaijan is updated

baseline.comment:
1) No targets available to measure the loss of biodiversity and ecosystem functionality in the agriculture, forestry, tourism, trade, travel and transport and fishery sectors;
2) No working group is established;
3) No national targets in response to Global Aichi targets have been developed;
4) NBSAP is out of date and does not consider newer guidance;
5) Clearing House Mechanism is not created

