target.comment:
1) The methodology for pasture inventory is prepared;
2) Inventory of the three thousand ha of summer pastures is applied;
3) Sustainable pasture management recommendations are prepared;
4) Pasture restoration activities started.

1) Carbon monitoring system is created, at least 8 specialists trained in carbon monitoring tracking system;
2) Pasture restoration activities in approximately 3000 ha of pilot territory are completed;
3) At least 15 farmer organizations have started implementation of the management recommendations for sustainable use of pasture resources.

actual.comment:
1) Carbon monitoring system were created, more than 20 experts trained in carbon monitoring tracking system;
2) Pasture restoration activities in approximately 3000 ha of pilot territory are completed; the rehabilitation works in 9 farms has been finalized and in 7 farms will be continued next year. 
3) Management plans for 16 farms based on local approach were prepared.
